{"tid":1219393,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"各位幫手瞭解下佢哋嘅前世今生，可能佢哋祖家鄉里都想知呢","createTime":"2019-06-13T19:55:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T20:27:39.000Z","uid":260806,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f346975c002ba0f2f11870689a7d5dc1931bb8dd","tid":1219393,"uid":260806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T19:55:54.000Z","msg":"「6.12大清場」現場主要由3應變大隊負責指揮，其中新界南總區應變大隊主力負責守衛添華道立法會大樓方向防線，由該區指揮官外籍總警司陶輝（Rupert Dover）率領；而江敏強則率領新界北總區負責行政長官辦公室現場指揮。據消息稱，當時立法會大樓外率先爆發衝突，警方亦因此打出「第一槍」。根據資料，陶輝當年亦曾參與處理佔領運動的「Solarpeak行動」，事後獲港府表揚表現出色的10名警官之一，獲嘉許「行政長官公共服務獎狀」，而同時莊定賢亦有份獲表揚。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190613/59711209\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190613%2F59711209&d=dLzfXDqznxc4YuOEPdKADbktNrE0CDS5yYjP391fFHI%3D&h=c67fc90b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190613%2F59711209&h=b941dd0d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190613/59711209</a><br />\n<br />\n至於「速龍小隊」則由警察機動部隊校長外籍總警司莊定賢（David Jordon）全權主理。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/mm.dbchk/videos/732212416892417/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fmm.dbchk%2Fvideos%2F732212416892417%2F&d=dLzfXDqznxc4YuOEPdKADbktNrE0CDS5yYjP391fFHI%3D&h=2bbf0e71\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/mm.dbchk/videos/732212416892417/</a>"},{"pid":"ca909cb4131fc633447f1897a7866b7efac7d7f6","tid":1219393,"uid":171650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T20:27:39.000Z","msg":"推"}]}